<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Contraception Methods</h2>
    <p class="text-center mb-5">Contraception effectiveness is typically measured by both "perfect use" (when used exactly as directed) and "typical use" (accounting for human error).</p>
    
